column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/dc0f4dfebf05e7b9261b593302cb3a01ab12d767 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu
How is someone supposed to drop a URL into the client without it being shown already? :p\n
